                magnam ex vel dolorem voluptate id ducimus. Placeat porro doloribus
                cumque veniam hic atque quas maiores.
            </p>
            <div class="s3-link">
                <a href="~/Home/Contact" class="btn btn-1">Contatez nous</a>
                <a href="~/Home/About" class="btn btn-2">A propos</a>
            </div>
        </div>
